articles.title: Samsung Pay just lost its best feature on the Galaxy S21
articles.description: Samsung has removed MST, or magnetic secure transmission, from the US editions of the Galaxy S21 phone and all future Galaxy phones sold in the US. This feature let you pay at almost any terminal, even ones that don't support NFC or mobile payments.
